*
# Track the short-overview deliverable + this directory's README.
# Whitelist the dir AND its contents recursively (the trailing `/**`
# is required when the surrounding `*` pattern would otherwise
# re-ignore descendants of an un-ignored directory).
!README.md
!.gitignore
!short_overview/
!short_overview/**
# Don't track generated previews / pycaches inside the unignored subdir.
short_overview/walkthrough_preview.png
short_overview/__pycache__/
